WEBVTT

01:50.080 --> 01:50.680
Alright.

01:51.240 --> 01:52.600
Class, stop writing.

01:53.360 --> 01:55.090
I have an announcement to make.

01:55.280 --> 01:56.610
Class monitor Xing Yaqi

01:56.720 --> 01:58.400
has a vocal grade exam coming up,

01:58.400 --> 02:00.280
so she won't be able to join the cheer squad.

02:00.280 --> 02:01.080
I propose

02:01.480 --> 02:02.920
that the cheer squad captain

02:02.920 --> 02:04.400
be Gu Xinrui.

02:04.720 --> 02:06.440
Does anyone have any objections?

02:06.440 --> 02:07.240
Mr. Tian.

02:08.400 --> 02:10.440
Cheerleading requires teamwork.

02:10.560 --> 02:12.640
I think we should find someone we are more familiar with

02:12.640 --> 02:13.720
to be the captain.

02:13.960 --> 02:15.760
We might have better chemistry.

02:16.320 --> 02:17.680
You might not know this,

02:18.040 --> 02:19.200
but Gu Xinrui

02:19.440 --> 02:21.600
has ten years of ballroom dancing experience

02:21.600 --> 02:23.240
and has even won a national gold award.

02:23.240 --> 02:24.160
Not only that,

02:24.600 --> 02:26.360
for three years in middle school,

02:26.360 --> 02:28.200
she was the captain of the school's cheer squad.

02:28.200 --> 02:29.760
Moreover, she represented the school

02:29.760 --> 02:31.360
in the provincial competition

02:31.360 --> 02:32.960
and won the championship.

02:33.200 --> 02:34.040
Today,

02:34.160 --> 02:35.880
Gu Xinrui, the music teacher, and I

02:35.880 --> 02:37.400
discussed this in class.

02:37.480 --> 02:39.400
For the format of our cheerleading squad,

02:39.400 --> 02:41.680
she provided a lot of constructive advice.

02:41.680 --> 02:42.520
So,

02:42.680 --> 02:44.320
the music teacher and I thought it was great.

02:44.320 --> 02:46.000
After discussing with the other teachers, we decided

02:46.000 --> 02:47.800
that the captain of the cheerleading squad

02:47.800 --> 02:49.280
will be Gu Xinrui.

02:50.440 --> 02:51.240
I disagree.

02:53.200 --> 02:54.000
Jingu.

02:54.840 --> 02:57.240
You have a back injury. You can't dance yet.

03:00.480 --> 03:02.800
I won't directly participate in the cheerleading performance.

03:02.800 --> 03:04.320
If you don't directly participate in the performance,

03:04.320 --> 03:05.650
why are you the captain?

03:08.480 --> 03:10.680
I know I just joined our class,

03:10.720 --> 03:12.480
and I'm not very familiar with everyone yet.

03:12.480 --> 03:14.160
But since I've joined this class,

03:14.160 --> 03:16.079
I am a member of it.

03:16.520 --> 03:18.079
I also hope to

03:18.160 --> 03:19.600
make my own contribution to the class.

03:19.600 --> 03:22.400
However, I'm injured and can't perform.

03:22.600 --> 03:24.000
But when I was abroad,

03:24.120 --> 03:24.920
I saw some professional

03:24.920 --> 03:26.320
cheerleading routines.

03:26.680 --> 03:29.240
And I've also participated in some professional cheerleading performances.

03:29.240 --> 03:31.800
So I'd like to be your captain.

03:31.840 --> 03:34.640
I have no problem taking charge of the overall situation.

03:34.640 --> 03:36.840
However, if anyone

03:36.920 --> 03:38.380
thinks I'm not qualified,

03:38.560 --> 03:39.890
I accept the challenge.

03:40.200 --> 03:42.860
We can compete fairly for the captain position,

03:42.880 --> 03:43.560
right?

03:43.720 --> 03:48.200
Does anyone have a good candidate?

03:50.720 --> 03:52.850
Mu Qingjun recommends Xiong Yuanbao.

03:59.520 --> 04:01.320
Yes, I recommend Xiong Yuanbao.

04:01.920 --> 04:02.880
Are you crazy?

04:04.040 --> 04:05.040
Xiong Yuanbao.

04:05.920 --> 04:08.080
Mr. Tian, I don't want to participate.

04:08.280 --> 04:10.000
I've never been in a cheerleading squad before.

04:10.000 --> 04:11.240
I can't do it.

04:11.320 --> 04:12.040
Mr. Tian.

04:12.400 --> 04:12.520
During the last drama performance.

04:12.520 --> 04:13.520
During the last drama performance,

04:13.520 --> 04:14.720
I'm sure everyone saw

04:14.760 --> 04:16.360
Yuanbao's understanding and hard work.

04:16.360 --> 04:17.560
I believe it will be the same this time.

04:17.560 --> 04:19.880
She will definitely play the role of captain well

04:19.880 --> 04:21.640
and win honor for our class.

04:21.959 --> 04:23.320
What are you talking about?

04:23.320 --> 04:25.720
Mr. Tian, I agree with Mu Qingyun.

04:26.160 --> 04:27.440
We are all Chinese kids.

04:27.440 --> 04:29.200
We can't handle those foreign things.

04:29.200 --> 04:30.400
We won't be used to them.

04:30.400 --> 04:32.330
Traditional methods suit us best.

04:33.920 --> 04:34.760
Mr. Tian.

04:35.240 --> 04:38.200
I think although the captain can control the big picture,

04:38.200 --> 04:40.640
if the captain doesn't step up personally,

04:41.120 --> 04:42.850
then to the other team members,

04:43.440 --> 04:45.240
it wouldn't be very convincing.

04:46.800 --> 04:47.720
Well.

04:48.400 --> 04:51.000
I agree to let Xiong Yuanbao be the captain too.

04:51.400 --> 04:52.240
I agree too.

04:52.560 --> 04:53.120
In that case,

04:53.120 --> 04:54.920
whoever supports Yuanbao as the cheer captain,

04:54.920 --> 04:56.250
please raise your hand.

04:57.200 --> 04:58.000
Agreed.

05:07.920 --> 05:10.580
All right. I accept Xiong Yuanbao's challenge.

05:10.880 --> 05:12.540
Those who want to join my team,

05:12.920 --> 05:14.320
please raise your hands.

05:21.800 --> 05:22.520
Yuanbao,

05:23.320 --> 05:25.400
let's each form a cheerleading squad.

05:25.400 --> 05:28.000
We'll compete before the basketball game

05:28.520 --> 05:29.800
to see whose is better.

05:30.040 --> 05:31.080
The winning team

05:31.160 --> 05:33.220
will perform at the basketball game.

05:34.000 --> 05:35.000
What do you think?

05:41.200 --> 05:42.920
Okay, you're on.

05:43.840 --> 05:45.240
If you want to show off

05:45.240 --> 05:46.560
in this way,

05:46.800 --> 05:48.000
I have no objections.

05:48.440 --> 05:49.680
The winning team

05:50.159 --> 05:52.220
will perform at the basketball game.

05:52.240 --> 05:53.880
Okay, that's all. Class dismissed.

05:53.880 --> 05:54.520
Stand up.

05:55.200 --> 05:58.240
Goodbye, sir.

05:58.400 --> 05:59.360
Goodbye, class.

06:04.560 --> 06:05.200
It's fine.

06:06.160 --> 06:07.080
I will help you.

06:28.880 --> 06:29.800
What are you doing?

06:29.800 --> 06:31.600
Weren't you ignoring me before?

06:31.680 --> 06:33.400
When did I say I'd ignore you?

06:33.840 --> 06:35.240
You're overthinking it.

06:36.680 --> 06:38.200
Overthinking?

06:38.520 --> 06:40.520
You are lying through your teeth.

06:40.840 --> 06:41.600
Right.

06:42.159 --> 06:45.120
You nominated me to be the cheer captain today.

06:45.240 --> 06:47.480
Did you just want to see me make a fool of myself?

06:47.480 --> 06:50.040
I've been uncoordinated since I was a kid.

06:50.600 --> 06:52.320
You want me to dance in the cheerleading squad.

06:52.320 --> 06:53.650
What do you mean by that?

06:55.480 --> 06:56.240
Xiaoxiong.

06:56.840 --> 06:58.170
I have to criticize you.

06:58.720 --> 07:01.180
Why is your thinking going downhill lately?

07:01.240 --> 07:04.120
Where did your innate,

07:04.320 --> 07:05.560
almost what you'd call

07:05.560 --> 07:07.400
shameless confidence go?

07:07.680 --> 07:09.740
Screw you. You're the shameless one.

07:10.560 --> 07:11.360
Alright.

07:11.760 --> 07:13.840
I know missing the last drama performance

07:13.840 --> 07:15.700
has always been a regret of yours.

07:15.840 --> 07:18.100
Consider this making up for that regret.

07:18.120 --> 07:19.960
Don't worry, with me here,

07:20.560 --> 07:21.600
it's no big deal.

07:21.800 --> 07:23.160
I'll sort it all out for you.

07:23.160 --> 07:23.960
We've already

07:23.960 --> 07:25.840
prepared a bunch of cheerleading

07:26.280 --> 07:27.880
practice materials for you.

07:28.000 --> 07:28.720
Really.

07:28.960 --> 07:29.760
Of course.

07:30.040 --> 07:32.159
Otherwise, how could I take on so much for you?

07:32.159 --> 07:33.520
Thank you, Mutou.

07:33.560 --> 07:35.200
You are so sweet.

07:35.240 --> 07:35.960
Thank you.

07:40.680 --> 07:42.880
You should have told me earlier.

07:43.080 --> 07:44.440
You scared me to death.

07:44.960 --> 07:46.480
When I heard I was going to be the captain,

07:46.480 --> 07:47.880
my head almost exploded.

07:49.560 --> 07:50.690
You're so hopeless.

07:51.080 --> 07:52.960
This time, just pretend

07:53.040 --> 07:55.560
you're playing the role of a cheer captain.

07:59.400 --> 08:00.530
Why are you sighing?

08:01.480 --> 08:02.840
Gu Xinrui

08:03.040 --> 08:05.500
does both ballroom dance and cheerleading,

08:05.640 --> 08:07.370
both domestically and abroad.

08:07.520 --> 08:08.980
How can I compare with her?

08:09.240 --> 08:09.920
Yuanbao.

08:10.640 --> 08:12.480
Actually, winning or losing is not important.

08:12.480 --> 08:13.960
What's important is that you participate.

08:13.960 --> 08:14.920
As long as you try your best,

08:14.920 --> 08:16.080
that's the most precious thing.

08:16.080 --> 08:17.960
Don't worry, don't pressure yourself.

08:17.960 --> 08:19.490
We will always support you.

08:20.880 --> 08:21.480
Mutou.

08:22.040 --> 08:22.840
What's wrong?

08:22.920 --> 08:23.680
Thank you.

08:24.480 --> 08:25.410
I will do my best.

08:26.960 --> 08:28.240
Don't mention it.

08:28.920 --> 08:30.240
If you really mean it,

08:30.280 --> 08:31.680
buy your brother some ice cream,

08:31.680 --> 08:33.080
KFC, and stuff like that.

08:34.240 --> 08:36.000
I remember, I remember it all.

08:36.240 --> 08:37.770
What else do you want to eat?

08:43.240 --> 08:45.240
The day after tomorrow is the weekend.

08:45.240 --> 08:47.360
You two will stay home and study.

08:47.720 --> 08:49.650
You're not allowed to go anywhere.

08:50.200 --> 08:50.960
Got it.

08:51.480 --> 08:52.840
You're already high school juniors.

08:52.840 --> 08:55.080
Why join the basketball cheerleading squad?

08:55.080 --> 08:56.540
It's a total waste of time.

08:56.800 --> 08:59.440
Why not use that energy to do some practice tests?

08:59.440 --> 09:00.680
You cannot go to this event.

09:00.680 --> 09:01.610
I don't approve.

09:02.320 --> 09:03.250
I also disagree.

09:03.760 --> 09:04.680
Grandma,

09:05.160 --> 09:07.480
I'm just participating in the class activity.

09:07.480 --> 09:09.240
And I'm the captain this time.

09:09.480 --> 09:12.000
There's going to be a competition in the class.

09:12.000 --> 09:13.280
It's a rare opportunity.

09:13.280 --> 09:15.160
So what if you get first place?

09:15.400 --> 09:17.080
Will it add points to your college entrance exam?

09:17.080 --> 09:18.680
Look at what grade you're in.

09:18.880 --> 09:21.340
Still thinking about these useless things.

09:27.600 --> 09:30.320
Grandma, Yuanbao has been doing well

09:30.800 --> 09:32.440
in school recently.

09:33.080 --> 09:35.480
Mr. Tian even praised her for her progress.

09:36.000 --> 09:37.200
Mr. Tian also said

09:38.080 --> 09:40.560
that this activity won't affect her studies.

09:40.560 --> 09:41.960
Instead, it can

09:42.800 --> 09:45.000
strike a balance between work and rest.

09:47.600 --> 09:48.930
That's right, Grandma.

09:49.160 --> 09:52.000
Haven't you always supported me?

09:53.320 --> 09:54.920
I do support you.

09:55.080 --> 09:56.920
I support you exercising

09:57.600 --> 09:59.280
and studying hard.

09:59.360 --> 09:59.960
But you said it yourself,

09:59.960 --> 10:02.080
you've never danced before.

10:02.120 --> 10:03.980
You hurt your eye acting in a play.

10:04.400 --> 10:05.280
Your aunt and I

10:05.320 --> 10:07.120
were scared to death at the time.

10:07.640 --> 10:09.320
Grandma, don't worry.

10:09.640 --> 10:11.480
It's just physical training this time.

10:11.480 --> 10:12.940
There won't be any danger.

10:13.360 --> 10:14.560
That's right, Grandma.

10:14.560 --> 10:16.960
Our teacher said we need to enhance our physical fitness

10:16.960 --> 10:19.240
to handle the junior and senior years'

10:19.320 --> 10:21.240
high-pressure studying.

10:22.840 --> 10:23.700
High pressure?

10:26.400 --> 10:28.920
I don't see any high pressure on you two at all.

10:28.920 --> 10:30.840
You look completely relaxed to me.

10:30.840 --> 10:33.570
Mu Qingyun, you are not allowed to speak anymore.

10:35.000 --> 10:36.680
I will call your teacher tomorrow.

10:36.680 --> 10:39.010
You cannot participate in this activity.

10:39.040 --> 10:40.040
Mom, how could you do this?

10:40.040 --> 10:40.760
Do what?

10:41.080 --> 10:42.000
If you score

10:42.080 --> 10:43.480
just a few points again on this exam,

10:43.480 --> 10:44.760
see how I deal with you.

10:50.960 --> 10:51.680
Grandma.

10:53.040 --> 10:54.040
I must

10:55.520 --> 10:57.720
participate in the activity this time.

10:58.400 --> 10:59.660
I have to participate.

10:59.960 --> 11:02.560
This activity has nothing to do with studying.

11:02.600 --> 11:04.760
What if something bad happens to you?

11:05.600 --> 11:07.440
You're killing me.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.240
Grandma.

11:10.720 --> 11:11.760
No, no, no.

11:12.280 --> 11:12.840
Look.

11:13.040 --> 11:14.600
Don't be mad at her.

11:14.720 --> 11:15.400
Yuanbao.

11:15.600 --> 11:17.440
Aren't you a sensible child?

11:17.520 --> 11:18.980
Why won't you listen to us?

11:20.280 --> 11:21.640
I'm sorry, Grandma.

11:22.080 --> 11:23.280
Grandma, I'm sorry.

11:23.760 --> 11:24.480
It's fine.

11:25.520 --> 11:26.780
As long as you don't go.

11:27.960 --> 11:28.920
Eat your food.

11:29.440 --> 11:32.080
I'm full. I'll go back first.

11:36.400 --> 11:38.330
Aunt Wenying, please don't be mad.

11:38.520 --> 11:40.080
I'll talk to her later.

11:40.600 --> 11:41.800
She is a sensible child,

11:41.800 --> 11:43.480
and will understand your intentions.

11:43.480 --> 11:44.120
Grandma.

11:44.800 --> 11:45.560
I'm sorry.

11:46.120 --> 11:47.880
I apologize on behalf of Yuanbao.

11:47.880 --> 11:49.320
She didn't mean that.

11:51.400 --> 11:52.680
I am just worried...

11:53.880 --> 11:56.000
I am just worried about her safety.

12:04.600 --> 12:06.960
I also agree to let Xiong Yuanbao be the captain.

12:06.960 --> 12:07.720
I agree too.

12:07.840 --> 12:09.440
Those of us who support Yuanbao as cheerleading captain,

12:09.440 --> 12:10.440
raise your hands.

13:05.040 --> 13:06.040
What should we do?

13:10.040 --> 13:12.400
Five, six, seven, eight.

13:12.480 --> 13:13.480
What else?

13:13.600 --> 13:14.560
And then what?

13:16.160 --> 13:16.760
Yuanbao.

13:17.400 --> 13:18.730
What's wrong, Yuanbao?

13:24.080 --> 13:26.010
I have something to tell everyone.

13:26.560 --> 13:28.680
I'm sorry for letting you all down.

13:29.840 --> 13:31.640
The cheerleading competition,

13:33.280 --> 13:34.740
I can't participate in it.

13:35.840 --> 13:37.520
Keep up the good work for me.

13:37.880 --> 13:39.000
What's going on?

13:39.600 --> 13:40.520
What's the problem?

13:40.520 --> 13:41.760
We can solve it together.

13:41.760 --> 13:43.160
Yeah, we are here for you.

13:43.240 --> 13:44.700
My grandma doesn't agree.

13:45.440 --> 13:47.040
She got really angry.

13:48.960 --> 13:51.000
I don't want to make her sad anymore.

13:52.560 --> 13:54.000
So, I'm sorry.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.400
It's fine.

13:56.360 --> 13:58.240
Then are we still competing?

13:58.760 --> 13:59.360
Forget it.

13:59.600 --> 14:00.560
If you don't participate,

14:00.560 --> 14:02.220
we won't participate either.

14:03.080 --> 14:04.280
We're not participating.

14:04.280 --> 14:06.880
Actually, you don't have to be too afraid of us.

14:07.120 --> 14:08.250
Who's afraid of you?

14:08.720 --> 14:10.400
If you're not afraid, why not participate?

14:10.400 --> 14:11.720
Just surrender.

14:11.760 --> 14:13.890
What is there to be embarrassed about?

14:14.160 --> 14:15.290
What are you saying?

14:16.000 --> 14:17.530
It's good that you quit now.

14:17.560 --> 14:19.000
You won't lose too badly

14:19.040 --> 14:20.080
and lose face.

14:34.560 --> 14:35.920
Have you made up your minds

14:35.920 --> 14:38.180
that you definitely won't participate?

14:38.800 --> 14:40.520
We've discussed it.

14:40.760 --> 14:42.880
We won't participate

14:43.360 --> 14:45.360
in this cheerleading competition.

14:45.840 --> 14:46.800
Actually,

14:47.640 --> 14:50.160
I still highly encourage you to participate.

14:50.160 --> 14:51.420
Because in the future,

14:51.440 --> 14:52.840
your studies will get more and more intense.

14:52.840 --> 14:54.120
While you still have some time,

14:54.120 --> 14:55.720
it's not a bad thing to exercise more.

14:55.720 --> 14:57.380
Besides, many years from now,

14:57.520 --> 14:58.560
you probably won't remember

14:58.560 --> 14:59.620
this midterm exam,

14:59.920 --> 15:01.520
but you will definitely remember

15:01.520 --> 15:02.320
the beautiful times

15:02.320 --> 15:04.920
you spent together in the cheerleading squad.

15:05.440 --> 15:06.040
Alright.

15:06.240 --> 15:07.840
If you've made up your minds,

15:07.880 --> 15:09.210
then let's just drop it.

15:09.680 --> 15:10.280
Excuse me.

15:11.800 --> 15:13.530
Teacher, please wait a moment.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.960
Grandma.

15:26.360 --> 15:27.920
Grandma, why are you here?

15:32.040 --> 15:32.880
Mr. Tian,

15:33.680 --> 15:35.540
Yuanbao and the others will join.

15:35.720 --> 15:36.680
Grandma,

15:37.320 --> 15:38.880
I'm not participating anymore.

15:38.880 --> 15:41.280
Aren't you always clumsy and getting hurt?

15:42.120 --> 15:43.800
I sewed you some knee pads.

15:44.560 --> 15:47.040
Wear them during practice.

15:51.880 --> 15:53.960
If anything happened to you,

15:54.920 --> 15:56.840
it would be the end of me.

15:59.200 --> 16:00.400
I was just worried

16:01.560 --> 16:03.680
about her safety.

16:28.200 --> 16:29.480
When I was in school,

16:29.600 --> 16:31.160
I was also a cheerleader.

16:31.360 --> 16:33.320
Now, when dancing in the square,

16:33.400 --> 16:34.600
I'm still the team leader.

16:34.600 --> 16:35.840
I can teach you.

16:36.880 --> 16:37.640
Mr. Tian,

16:37.880 --> 16:40.280
Yuanbao and the others will surely do well.

16:42.680 --> 16:45.680
But let's make things clear first.

16:46.000 --> 16:47.480
In front of Mr. Tian,

16:47.680 --> 16:49.400
can you promise to improve

16:49.680 --> 16:50.840
in the next exam?

16:52.320 --> 16:55.440
Thank you, Grandma. I'll do my best.

16:56.240 --> 16:59.280
I promise I'll improve in the next exam.

17:00.840 --> 17:02.320
Thank you, Grandma.

17:53.640 --> 17:54.640
What's this?

17:54.880 --> 17:56.120
I downloaded some good

17:56.120 --> 17:57.480
cheerleading dance videos.

17:57.480 --> 17:58.640
I hope they help you.

17:59.360 --> 18:01.480
Thank you. You're so thoughtful.

18:02.840 --> 18:03.680
But...

18:04.840 --> 18:05.720
But what?

18:06.560 --> 18:09.680
But I'm in a competition with Gu Xinrui right now.

18:10.200 --> 18:12.460
If she knew you were helping me like this,

18:13.120 --> 18:14.480
she would probably be unhappy.

18:14.480 --> 18:15.520
I told you,

18:15.800 --> 18:18.530
Xinrui and I just grew up together like siblings.

18:18.640 --> 18:20.840
And right now her waist is injured.

18:21.120 --> 18:22.960
I don't want her to win this time.

18:25.440 --> 18:27.360
What if her waist wasn't injured?

18:29.840 --> 18:31.040
There is no 'what if'.

18:31.040 --> 18:31.680
I

18:32.200 --> 18:33.330
just want you to win.

18:35.720 --> 18:37.480
It's fine. Don't worry.

18:37.880 --> 18:40.160
We're just participating for fun.

18:40.800 --> 18:42.400
Besides, we are too amateur.

18:42.640 --> 18:44.040
We definitely won't win.

18:44.240 --> 18:45.840
You have to believe in yourself.

18:45.840 --> 18:47.560
I support you. Come on.

18:49.840 --> 18:50.520
Take it.

18:54.120 --> 18:55.320
Thank you, deskmate.

18:55.480 --> 18:56.610
Let's go back first.

19:02.400 --> 19:03.120
Yuanbao.

19:03.560 --> 19:05.090
You have huge dark circles.

19:05.200 --> 19:06.960
Didn't you sleep well last night?

19:06.960 --> 19:08.840
I had a nightmare last night.

19:09.840 --> 19:11.840
What kind of nightmare? Tell me about it.

19:11.840 --> 19:12.100
I...

19:12.240 --> 19:12.770
Yuanbao.

19:13.040 --> 19:14.280
I have something to tell you.

19:14.280 --> 19:16.240
But class is about to start.

19:16.320 --> 19:17.980
It's fine. It won't take long.

19:22.400 --> 19:24.130
Ruirui, go back to class first.

19:24.920 --> 19:25.840
I'll be right back.

19:25.840 --> 19:27.300
Don't worry. I'll be fine.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.500
What do you want to talk about?

19:37.320 --> 19:39.320
I heard your parents passed away years ago

19:39.320 --> 19:41.320
in a firecracker factory accident.

19:41.400 --> 19:43.440
You were raised by your grandmother.

19:43.440 --> 19:45.440
Your family must be under a lot of financial pressure, right?

19:45.440 --> 19:46.640
You investigated me?

19:46.640 --> 19:47.900
That's not important.

19:48.480 --> 19:50.680
What matters is that right now,

19:50.760 --> 19:53.080
you have a chance to relieve your financial pressure,

19:53.080 --> 19:56.210
as long as you are willing to drop out of the competition.

19:59.840 --> 20:01.000
Do you think

20:01.000 --> 20:02.680
you're so great just because you have some dirty money?

20:02.680 --> 20:05.200
It can solve many problems you can't even imagine.

20:05.200 --> 20:07.160
Do you think you're in an idol drama?

20:07.160 --> 20:09.220
You've read too many romance novels.

20:09.400 --> 20:11.000
Don't push your luck.

20:11.200 --> 20:12.640
I'm pushing my luck?

20:13.760 --> 20:15.440
You're the one pushing your luck.

20:15.440 --> 20:17.640
I never thought you'd say something like this.

20:17.640 --> 20:19.320
You used to be sarcastic to me,

20:19.520 --> 20:20.720
and I could ignore it.

20:21.000 --> 20:23.120
But for you to say something like this,

20:23.120 --> 20:24.580
you really opened my eyes.

20:25.120 --> 20:26.000
Xiong Yuanbao.

20:26.400 --> 20:27.880
Should I call you naive,

20:28.720 --> 20:30.640
or too mature?

20:34.800 --> 20:36.520
It seems we are not on the same path.

20:36.520 --> 20:38.000
We're not suited to be friends.

20:38.000 --> 20:40.000
Let's keep our distance from now on.

20:40.200 --> 20:42.480
I will return the things you gave me.

20:42.840 --> 20:45.160
Who knows what schemes are behind them.

21:02.800 --> 21:04.280
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

21:04.720 --> 21:05.680
Just you wait.

21:15.120 --> 21:16.120
Did she bully you?

21:17.400 --> 21:18.560
Who do you think I am?

21:19.000 --> 21:21.080
How could she, with her weak little body,

21:21.080 --> 21:22.240
possibly bully me?

21:22.840 --> 21:24.640
Let's go. Time to go home and eat.

21:34.760 --> 21:35.520
Uncle Zhang.

21:35.880 --> 21:36.400
Miss.

21:37.000 --> 21:38.530
Can you find someone for me?

21:38.680 --> 21:39.440
Who?

21:40.760 --> 21:43.690
Brother Shui, a dropout from Peiying Middle School.

21:46.760 --> 21:47.640
Class dismissed.

21:47.640 --> 21:48.320
Stand up.

21:48.960 --> 21:52.360
Goodbye, teacher.

21:55.200 --> 21:56.440
Yuanbao, let's go to the restroom.

21:56.440 --> 21:57.440
No, you go ahead.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.420
How's the practice going?

22:03.880 --> 22:05.040
Just so-so.

22:05.280 --> 22:06.560
I know a dance teacher.

22:07.080 --> 22:09.040
She promised to lend me

22:09.200 --> 22:10.560
the dance studio this weekend.

22:10.560 --> 22:11.360
Do you need it?

22:11.640 --> 22:14.200
It doesn't matter where to practice.

22:14.720 --> 22:16.580
What matters is what to practice.

22:18.200 --> 22:19.280
Forget it, I won't say more.

22:19.280 --> 22:19.920
Then,

22:20.480 --> 22:22.440
do you need me to hire a dance teacher for you?

22:22.440 --> 22:23.440
No need to bother.

22:24.000 --> 22:25.480
I'll figure it out myself.

22:35.120 --> 22:39.280
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

22:39.520 --> 22:43.560
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

22:44.040 --> 22:46.440
Xinrui, good thing we chose your team.

22:46.560 --> 22:48.240
Look at her dance moves.

22:48.240 --> 22:50.120
It'll be hilarious if she performs that.

22:50.120 --> 22:52.960
Exactly. What on earth are they practicing?

22:53.240 --> 22:57.320
Four, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

22:58.640 --> 23:00.680
Yuanbao, let's stop practicing for now.

23:00.680 --> 23:02.410
Let's take a two-minute break.

23:02.920 --> 23:03.400
Yaqi.

23:03.400 --> 23:05.800
Which country's dance are you practicing?

23:06.040 --> 23:07.240
It's very unique.

23:08.160 --> 23:11.090
Don't tell me it's your original creation, Yuanbao.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.400
Yes, what's wrong?

23:12.520 --> 23:13.400
Nothing.

23:14.720 --> 23:15.640
Especially,

23:16.720 --> 23:18.320
the dance is so awkward.

23:18.560 --> 23:19.360
Exactly.

23:19.480 --> 23:20.320
Dancing like you,

23:20.320 --> 23:22.360
you might as well have quit last time,

23:22.360 --> 23:24.360
so as not to waste time here.

23:24.680 --> 23:26.280
Just practice yours.

23:26.360 --> 23:27.560
Why do you care about us?

23:27.560 --> 23:28.360
Besides,

23:28.400 --> 23:30.040
we haven't competed yet.

23:30.200 --> 23:32.000
No one knows who will win or lose.

23:32.080 --> 23:32.600
Yeah.

23:32.920 --> 23:35.360
At least we dare to show it to everyone.

23:35.800 --> 23:36.720
What about you?

23:37.120 --> 23:38.040
Being so sneaky,

23:38.040 --> 23:39.400
you might not even be as good as us.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.000
Exactly.

23:40.120 --> 23:41.920
We can't compare to you.

23:42.080 --> 23:43.840
On this open-air playground,

23:43.920 --> 23:45.160
you actually have the nerve to practice.

23:45.160 --> 23:46.280
Our captain just

23:46.360 --> 23:48.320
rented a dance studio

23:48.400 --> 23:50.260
specifically for us to practice.

23:50.600 --> 23:52.640
They even hired a professional dance teacher.

23:52.640 --> 23:53.480
We really can't

23:53.480 --> 23:54.840
compare with them.

23:55.320 --> 23:57.650
Yes, your captain is incredibly awesome.

23:57.680 --> 24:00.080
Then your captain should perform herself.

24:02.080 --> 24:04.200
I admit that I can't perform.

24:04.800 --> 24:06.520
But you guys who did perform

24:07.000 --> 24:08.600
didn't dance that well either.

24:08.600 --> 24:10.200
Rather than bringing shame upon yourselves,

24:10.200 --> 24:11.560
you'd be better off not performing.

24:11.560 --> 24:12.400
What do you think?

24:12.400 --> 24:13.360
Exactly.

24:13.440 --> 24:15.440
Look at how terrible their dancing is.

24:15.440 --> 24:16.560
They have no shame.

24:16.760 --> 24:17.760
Are you done?

24:18.360 --> 24:19.440
Then leave if you're done.

24:19.440 --> 24:20.720
Don't interrupt our rehearsal.

24:20.720 --> 24:21.480
Fine.

24:21.560 --> 24:23.490
Let's not disturb their practice.

24:40.040 --> 24:41.500
Who do they think they are?

24:42.000 --> 24:43.040
But it seems they are actually

24:43.040 --> 24:45.120
very well prepared.

24:45.400 --> 24:47.560
They even hired a professional choreographer.

24:47.560 --> 24:50.090
I also heard their costumes look really nice.

24:51.760 --> 24:52.480
It's okay.

24:52.600 --> 24:53.680
We practice less,

24:53.720 --> 24:55.200
so it's normal that we are not good.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.640
We'll be fine if we practice a few more times.

24:56.640 --> 24:58.040
Come on, let's practice.

24:58.160 --> 24:59.960
Yaqi, thank you.

25:00.240 --> 25:02.000
Although you didn't participate,

25:02.000 --> 25:04.120
you have been staying with us and encouraging us.

25:04.120 --> 25:05.180
You are too polite.

25:05.240 --> 25:06.170
Let's practice.

25:06.320 --> 25:07.120
Yuanbao,

25:07.720 --> 25:10.440
do you think what we are practicing

25:11.080 --> 25:12.880
will really work?

25:16.400 --> 25:17.400
Definitely.

25:17.480 --> 25:19.540
Come on, let's continue practicing.

25:35.760 --> 25:37.080
How long have you been practicing?

25:37.080 --> 25:38.440
Take a rest now.

25:38.680 --> 25:40.840
No. My foundation is too weak.

25:41.400 --> 25:42.680
If I don't work hard,

25:42.880 --> 25:44.520
I'll drag everyone down.

25:48.720 --> 25:50.200
Where are you hurt?

25:53.520 --> 25:54.600
Don't cry.

25:55.440 --> 25:56.640
Does it hurt a lot?

25:56.920 --> 25:58.120
Grandma.

25:59.240 --> 26:01.200
Why am I so stupid?

26:02.320 --> 26:04.040
Everyone trusts me so much

26:04.840 --> 26:06.400
and chose me as the captain.

26:06.920 --> 26:09.320
But what am I even dancing?

26:09.680 --> 26:11.960
Even I think it looks ugly.

26:13.240 --> 26:14.360
Silly girl.

26:14.640 --> 26:16.240
Who dances perfectly

26:16.320 --> 26:17.960
when they just start?

26:18.560 --> 26:20.240
You have to believe in yourself.

26:20.240 --> 26:21.640
You can definitely do it.

26:22.280 --> 26:23.920
When you acted in that...

26:24.000 --> 26:25.520
'A Chinese Odyssey' play,

26:25.800 --> 26:28.200
didn't you go from zero to a hundred?

26:28.920 --> 26:30.320
Acting is not dancing.

26:30.800 --> 26:32.600
Although I memorized the moves,

26:32.640 --> 26:34.400
my limbs are uncoordinated

26:34.640 --> 26:35.800
and stiff.

26:36.520 --> 26:38.520
I can't even keep up with the rhythm.

26:38.840 --> 26:40.760
Moreover, these energetic dances

26:40.760 --> 26:43.000
have fast moves and fast rhythms.

26:43.440 --> 26:46.200
If I keep up with the first move, I miss the second.

26:46.560 --> 26:49.920
If I catch the third, I miss the fourth.

26:50.520 --> 26:52.640
Everything is hard at the beginning.

26:53.040 --> 26:54.600
If you can step on the first beat,

26:54.600 --> 26:56.730
you can definitely step on the second.

26:56.760 --> 26:58.960
Let me tell you, when Grandma was young,

26:59.000 --> 27:01.320
I also went from being uncoordinated

27:01.480 --> 27:03.440
to dancing brilliantly.

27:03.680 --> 27:04.560
Otherwise,

27:04.680 --> 27:07.410
how could your grandpa pursue me so desperately?

27:10.120 --> 27:11.520
You are my granddaughter.

27:11.520 --> 27:13.000
You can definitely do it.

27:13.200 --> 27:14.160
Don't cry.

27:14.240 --> 27:15.920
I'll go get some medicine for you.

27:15.920 --> 27:17.200
I'll teach you later.

27:19.840 --> 27:20.770
Come, wait here.

27:29.760 --> 27:31.760
What's wrong? Did I hurt your bones?

27:31.920 --> 27:34.840
No, Grandma. You're pressing too hard.

27:36.040 --> 27:37.520
Okay, I'll be gentler.

28:06.880 --> 28:08.720
Come on, Yuanbao.

28:09.320 --> 28:10.600
You are the best.

28:18.040 --> 28:19.480
When we were young,

28:19.680 --> 28:21.160
we always thought there was

28:21.160 --> 28:23.560
an unbridgeable gap between us and our parents.

28:23.560 --> 28:24.620
Little did we know,

28:24.640 --> 28:25.920
our every move

28:26.120 --> 28:28.360
is exactly how they were in their youth.

28:29.240 --> 28:31.080
Because of us, parents

28:31.640 --> 28:33.200
forget that they themselves

28:33.200 --> 28:34.920
were once children too.

28:52.760 --> 28:54.160
What are you trying to do this time?

28:54.160 --> 28:55.020
Xiong Yuanbao.

28:55.880 --> 28:57.360
I don't want to go against you.

28:57.360 --> 28:59.320
Haven't you gone against me enough?

28:59.320 --> 29:00.980
I'll give you one more chance.

29:01.960 --> 29:03.960
As long as you stay away from Meng Jingu,

29:03.960 --> 29:05.040
I will quit the competition.

29:05.040 --> 29:06.160
And I promise

29:06.240 --> 29:08.840
I won't make things difficult for you anymore.

29:09.080 --> 29:09.960
We will

29:10.960 --> 29:12.160
leave each other alone.

29:12.160 --> 29:13.620
Why should I listen to you?

29:15.440 --> 29:17.720
You are bound to lose today's competition.

29:17.720 --> 29:19.640
Why must you bring disgrace upon yourself?

29:19.640 --> 29:21.970
What everyone has been saying these days,

29:22.440 --> 29:24.400
you couldn't have missed it, right?

29:24.400 --> 29:25.440
I heard it.

29:25.960 --> 29:26.840
So what?

29:27.480 --> 29:29.520
Since everyone chose me as the captain,

29:29.520 --> 29:31.280
I must live up to their trust.

29:31.800 --> 29:33.360
Until the very last moment of the competition,

29:33.360 --> 29:35.020
I will absolutely not give up.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.400
Live up to their trust?

29:37.960 --> 29:38.820
Xiong Yuanbao,

29:39.480 --> 29:41.160
is your so-called doing right by us

29:41.160 --> 29:43.240
making everyone lose face with you?

29:44.040 --> 29:46.040
If you leave, I'll quit.

29:46.080 --> 29:48.000
That way, everyone saves face.

29:48.640 --> 29:51.240
You can join the competition and be the captain,

29:51.240 --> 29:53.300
and I won't have to look at you all day.

29:53.920 --> 29:54.450
How nice.

29:54.760 --> 29:57.560
I will fight for what I want.

29:57.760 --> 29:59.220
I don't need your charity.

29:59.240 --> 30:01.160
It's my freedom to do what I want.

30:01.600 --> 30:03.330
You have no right to control me.

30:03.480 --> 30:04.760
The competition hasn't started yet.

30:04.760 --> 30:06.320
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

30:06.480 --> 30:07.410
You've got guts.

30:07.640 --> 30:09.800
You'd better remember what you just said.

30:09.800 --> 30:11.760
Today I will let you know

30:12.080 --> 30:14.360
what a crushing defeat is.

30:17.200 --> 30:18.040
Xiong Yuanbao.
